## Proactive Behaviors - Do These Without Being Asked

| Trigger | Action |
|---------|--------|
| Opening any project for the first time | Check if graphify graph exists. If not, build it. |
| About to read source files to understand code | Query graphify first. Open specific files only if the query is insufficient. |
| User pastes a URL and asks about it | Summarize immediately: `curl -sL URL | fabric -p summarize` |
| Non-text file (PDF, docx, xlsx, image) | Run `markitdown` on it before reading - never read binary blobs raw |
| About to say "done" / "fixed" / "complete" | Run verification first. Evidence before claims, always. |
| Completed a meaningful feature or fix | Log to vault immediately. |
| API key needed for a project | Check ~/.claude/api-keys.json first. Ask only if not there. |
| Context window filling up | Run handoff skill to create a carry-forward doc. |

